# Module: `packages/math`

- Pure functions only — no side effects, no external imports
- Always use the `Point` type from `types.ts` — never plain `{ x, y }`
- Functions must be unit-tested

## How to verify

- `grep -r "^import" packages/math/src/ | grep -v "from.*math\|from.*types"` — no external imports
- `grep -r "{ x:" packages/math/` — should use `Point` type, not plain objects
- `yarn test:app packages/math` — all math functions must have passing tests
